01:11:30,641 --> 01:11:31,868
Ayolah, Olaf.

1065
01:11:31,868 --> 01:11:36,830
Elsa mungkin dalam perjalanan
kembali saat ini, kita bisa ketemu dia dan...

1066
01:11:37,671 --> 01:11:39,499
Olaf?

1067
01:11:39,499 --> 01:11:42,420
Apa ini?
