1068
01:11:42,420 --> 01:11:44,779
Aku jatuh berguguran?

1069
01:11:44,779 --> 01:11:47,487
Tunggu, bukan. Bukan itu.

1070
01:11:48,905 --> 01:11:53,015
Aku jatuh berguguran.

1071
01:11:53,015 --> 01:11:56,445
Sihir di dalam diriku memudar.

1072
01:11:56,445 --> 01:11:58,053
Apa?

1073
01:11:59,250 --> 01:12:02,609
