1080
01:12:20,882 --> 01:12:22,739
Aku memegang mu.

1081
01:12:23,764 --> 01:12:25,862
Itu bagus.

1082
01:12:26,834 --> 01:12:28,889
Hei, Anna.

1083
01:12:28,889 --> 01:12:33,756
Aku baru saja pikirkan satu hal yang abadi.
-Apa itu?

1084
01:12:33,756 --> 01:12:35,892
Cinta.

1085
01:12:36,622 --> 01:12:38,918
Dekapan hangat?

1086
01:12:42,396 --> 01:12:45,468
Aku suka dekapan hangat.

1087
01:12:53,486 --> 01:12:55,317
Aku menyayangi mu.

1088
01:14:01,254 --> 01:14:04,269
Olaf, Elsa.

1089
01:14:05,638 --> 01:14:07,866
Apa yang harus ku lakukan sekarang?

1090
01:14:11,186 --> 01:14:13,921
♪ I've seen dark before ♪
