1091
01:14:13,921 --> 01:14:16,663
♪ But not like this ♪
Tapi tak seperti ini.

1092
01:14:16,663 --> 01:14:18,256
♪ This is cold ♪
Ini dingin.

1093
01:14:18,256 --> 01:14:19,804
♪ This is empty ♪
Ini hampa.

1094
01:14:19,804 --> 01:14:22,648
♪ This is numb ♪
Ini mati rasa.

1095
01:14:22,648 --> 01:14:25,295
♪ The life that I knew is over ♪
Hidup yang ku tahu telah berakhir.

1096
01:14:25,295 --> 01:14:27,544
♪ The lights are out ♪
Cahaya telah padam.

1097
01:14:27,544 --> 01:14:29,466
♪ Hello darkness ♪
Helo kegelapan.

1098
01:14:29,466 --> 01:14:32,699
♪ I'm ready to succumb ♪
Ku siap ntuk menyerah.

1099
01:14:34,271 --> 01:14:36,943
♪ I follow you around ♪
Aku ikuti mu kemanapun.

1100
01:14:36,943 --> 01:14:39,207
♪ I always have ♪
Yang selalu ku lakukan.

1101
01:14:39,207 --> 01:14:44,934
♪ But you've gone to a place I cannot find ♪
