1102
01:14:44,934 --> 01:14:47,246
♪ This grief ♪
Nestapa ini.

1103
01:14:47,246 --> 01:14:52,481
♪ has a gravity, it pulls me down ♪
Punya gravitasi, yang menarik ku ke bawah.

1104
01:14:55,463 --> 01:14:58,307
♪ But a tiny voice ♪
Tapi ada suara lirih.

1105
01:14:58,307 --> 01:15:02,907
♪ whispers in my mind ♪
