1106
01:15:03,544 --> 01:15:06,037
♪ You are lost ♪
Kau tersesat.

1107
01:15:06,037 --> 01:15:08,662
♪ Hope is gone ♪
Harapan telah sirna.

1108
01:15:08,662 --> 01:15:11,615
♪ But you must ♪
Tapi kau harus.

1109
01:15:11,615 --> 01:15:14,309
♪ Go on ♪
Terus melangkah.

1110
01:15:14,309 --> 01:15:19,058
♪ And do the next right thing ♪
