1111
01:15:26,197 --> 01:15:28,408
♪ Can there be a day ♪
Mungkinkah ada hari.

1112
01:15:28,408 --> 01:15:30,799
♪ beyond this night? ♪
Jauh di luar malam ini.

1113
01:15:30,799 --> 01:15:35,846
♪ I don't know anymore what is true ♪
Aku tak tahu lagi apa yang benar.

1114
01:15:35,846 --> 01:15:40,395
♪ I can't find my direction, I'm all alone ♪
Ku tak bisa temukan arahku. Aku hanya seorang diri.

1115
01:15:40,395 --> 01:15:46,887
♪ The only star that guided me was you ♪
Satu-satunya bintang yang tuntun aku adalah kau.

1116
01:15:46,887 --> 01:15:51,175
♪ How to rise from the floor? ♪
Bagaimana ku bangkit dari sini?

1117
01:15:51,175 --> 01:15:56,042
♪ When it's not you I'm rising for? ♪
Kalau bukan karna kaulah, aku bangkit.

1118
01:15:56,042 --> 01:16:00,791
♪ Just do the next right thing ♪
Hanya lakukan hal benar berikutnya.

1119
01:16:00,791 --> 01:16:02,932
♪ Take a step ♪
Ambil satu langkah.

1120
01:16:02,932 --> 01:16:05,250
♪ Step again ♪
Satu langkah lagi.

1121
01:16:05,250 --> 01:16:12,411
♪ It is all that I can to do.. ♪
Hanya ini yang aku bisa, ntuk lakukan...

1122
01:16:12,411 --> 01:16:16,776
♪ The next right thing ♪
Hal benar berikutnya.

1123
01:16:17,591 --> 01:16:21,950
♪ I won't look too far ahead ♪
Aku takkan melihat terlalu jauh ke depan.

1124
01:16:21,950 --> 01:16:25,751
♪ It's too much for me to take ♪
Terlalu berat untuk ku tanggung.

1125
01:16:25,751 --> 01:16:29,219
♪ But break it down to this next breath ♪
Tapi membaginya untuk tarikan nafas berikutnya.

1126
01:16:29,219 --> 01:16:31,329
♪ This next step ♪
Langkah berikut ini.

1127
01:16:31,329 --> 01:16:32,969
♪ This next choice ♪
Pilihan berikut ini.

1128
01:16:32,969 --> 01:16:37,420
♪ Is one that I can make ♪
adalah yang akan ku ambil.

1129
01:16:38,187 --> 01:16:42,632
♪ So I'll walk through this night ♪
Ku kan berjalan lalui malam ini.

1130
01:16:42,632 --> 01:16:47,426
♪ Stumbling blindly toward the light ♪
Terseok gapai ke arah cahaya.

1131
01:16:47,426 --> 01:16:52,513
♪ And do the next right thing ♪
Dan lakukan hal benar berikutnya.

1132
01:16:52,513 --> 01:16:57,279
♪ And with the dawn, what comes then? ♪
Dan bersama fajar, apa lagi selanjutnya?

1133
01:16:57,522 --> 01:16:58,820
♪ When it's clear ♪
Ketika semuanya jelas

1134
01:16:59,055 --> 01:17:04,186
♪ That everything will never be the same again? ♪
Kalau segalanya takkan pernah sama lagi.

1135
01:17:06,740 --> 01:17:09,776
♪ Then I'll make the choice ♪
Lalu ku kan buat pilihan.

1136
01:17:09,776 --> 01:17:13,416
♪ To hear that voice ♪
Ntuk dengarkan suara itu.

1137
01:17:13,416 --> 01:17:16,447
♪ And do ♪
Dan lakukan.

1138
01:17:16,447 --> 01:17:21,528
♪ The next right thing ♪
Hal benar berikutnya.

