1159
01:19:41,353 --> 01:19:44,799
Raja Runard telah mengkhianati semua orang.

1160
01:19:44,799 --> 01:19:46,251
Bagaimana kau tahu itu?

1161
01:19:46,251 --> 01:19:49,720
Kakakku telah berikan
nyawanya demi kebenaran.

1162
01:19:51,493 --> 01:19:52,789
Ku mohon.

1163
01:19:52,789 --> 01:19:55,011
Sebelum kita kehilangan nyawa banyak orang.

1164
01:20:17,211 --> 01:20:18,531
Awas!

1165
01:20:25,594 --> 01:20:27,633
Hancurkan bendungannya, Ayo!

1166
01:20:27,633 --> 01:20:29,878
Lemparkan batunya.

1167
01:20:34,437 --> 01:20:35,990
Ya, begitu.

1168
01:20:52,937 --> 01:20:53,871
Aku berhasil menangkapnya.

1169
01:20:53,871 --> 01:20:54,694
Anna.

1170
01:20:55,165 --> 01:20:57,318
